# Las Vegas Algorithm to solve ECDLP #

This repository contains the implementation of the Las Vegas Algorithm in C++. Serial and Parallel implementations are available.
ECDLP_Parallel and ECDLP_Serial directories contains the parallel and serial implementations respectively.

###Software dependencies :###
1) C/C++ compiler
2) OpemMPI
3) Number Theory Library (NTL) and GNU-GMP
4) Sage (to genetate inputs)

# Compiling the Code.#

## Parallel Code##
mpic++ *.cpp -lntl -lgmp -O3 -o ecdlp

## Serial Code ##
g++ *.cpp -lntl -lgmp -O3 -o ecdlp

